        {
            "_id": "n9RpO5CMZ9E4B8wI",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Rush and Steal",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Quickly moving in with grasping hands, the Stumpfield war saboteurs take what they can. The saboteurs Stride up to twice their Speed. During this movement, the saboteurs Interact to pick up an unattended object no larger than 2 Bulk or attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Steal] an item from a creature they're adjacent to; the goblins can pick up or Steal as many objects as they have remaining segments in any combination.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
